{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-06-22-1",
 "title": "Mustering for a Mock Dogfight",
 "summary": "In the hangar bay of the NRSC Deliverance, Colonel Altair Quila strides out in her flight gear and calls for volunteers to spar in the fighters. Bazil McKenzie, freshly back on duty and uncharacteristically in full uniform with new rank bars, eagerly accepts, surprising Altair. Commander Wedge proposes splitting into teams to test the green cadet Vek Eldar, offering to take Eldar on his wing, and Vek nervously agrees. The wary sergeant Lianna Blackledge consents to tune the fighters' capacitors down for a more realistic but less destructive mock battle, resigned to another busy stretch for her overworked techs.",
